.\">TAL:CA</a></span>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PTALF\" title=\"PetroTal Corp.\" target=\"_blank\">OTCQX:PTALF</a>) in the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4339457-petrotal-debt-free-oil-producer-intentions-to-pay-4-percent-dividend\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4339457-petrotal-debt-free-oil-producer-intentions-to-pay-4-percent-dividend\" target=\"_blank\">second quarter of 2020</a> when the oil price was hit very hard by the COVID pandemic. PetroTal survived and thrived, as the total return in the past 4.5 years comes</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2171537114/image_2171537114.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742482-petrotal-a-share-consolidation-should-help-this-big-yielding-oil-company", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 18:40:00"}, {"id": "4742898", "title": "TMV: A Levered Play Against Treasuries", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"An abstract drone/aerial view onto a colourful agricultural field\" data-id=\"1490953281\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"863px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1490953281/image_1490953281.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.co