s-returned\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener noopener noopener\">Last week,</a></em></strong> we discussed how speculation and leverage have returned in earnest to the market as investors rush to take on increasing levels of risk. With markets rising steadily all year, it is unsurprising to witness</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1132660268/image_1132660268.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742900-2025-do-economic-indicators-support-bullish-outlooks", "pub_date": "2024-12-08 18:10:00"}, {"id": "4742844", "title": "Snap: 25 Million Reasons To Love", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden 25M isolated on white background. 25M 3d. Thank you for 25 Million followers 3D gold. 3D rendering\" data-id=\"1499421143\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"886px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499421143/image_1499421143.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1